  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/715d9d8fcdb1d8662204bce40f639eb0.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village of Yugra hid an ancient and terrible secret behind its peaceful facade. The villagers' dreams of wealth unleashed a forgotten curse, turning their haven into a living hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your neighbors transform into unrecognizable monsters, you are left alone in the midst of this madness. Now, every door is a threat, every shadow an enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/7b27f02cca88f34fa8aefde30892289b.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive this nightmare:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> Secretly investigate the eerie homes of the cursed village to uncover the secrets within and find a path to salvation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide:</strong> Avoid being caught by the cursed homeowners as they undergo a horrifying transformation. They are not your neighbors anymore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect:</strong> Find the ancient artifacts required to break the curse and end this nightmare.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you save Yugra from this curse, or will you become just another one of its dark secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.poster.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.webm?t=1751594155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.mp4?t=1751594155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/715d9d8fcdb1d8662204bce40f639eb0.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village of Yugra hid an ancient and terrible secret behind its peaceful facade. The villagers' dreams of wealth unleashed a forgotten curse, turning their haven into a living hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your neighbors transform into unrecognizable monsters, you are left alone in the midst of this madness. Now, every door is a threat, every shadow an enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/7b27f02cca88f34fa8aefde30892289b.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive this nightmare:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> Secretly investigate the eerie homes of the cursed village to uncover the secrets within and find a path to salvation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hide:</strong> Avoid being caught by the cursed homeowners as they undergo a horrifying transformation. They are not your neighbors anymore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect:</strong> Find the ancient artifacts required to break the curse and end this nightmare.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you save Yugra from this curse, or will you become just another one of its dark secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.poster.avif?t=1751594155\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.webm?t=1751594155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405020/extras/c2364d475112af38ab323de5fcd739fb.mp4?t=1751594155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
